<varlistentry id="options.gtkrc20Path">
	<term>gtkrc20Path <emphasis remap='I'>path</emphasis></term>
	<listitem>
		<para>set fullfilename for gtkrc file to be generated by AfterStep from gtkrc-20_template
		on colorscheme changes. Default is ~/.gtkrc-2.0. Change to prevent mangling of your own gtkrc.
		More sensible approach is to edit the template.</para>
	</listitem>
</varlistentry>
